        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 15 - 17. Cunaxoidinae key illustrations. Setae are removed from figures 16 - 17 for clarity 15 a Idiosoma with poorly demarcated dorsal plates 15 b Idiosoma with well demarcated dorsal plates 16 a Pedipalp tibiotarsus with subapical process and small teeth present 16 b Pedipalp tibiotarsus with subapical process and small teeth absent 17 a Pedipalp tibiotarsus with a single pointed process 17 b Pedipalp tibiotarsus with two pointed processes." ;
